description:
List of largest sports contracts.

###**COLUMN DESCRIPTION**
- 'rank': rank of the person. Repeated values for the same person indicate a tie.
- 'name': name of the person
- 'org': organization
- 'sport': name of the sport
- 'contract_val': contract value in USD
- 'avg_per_year': average per year in USD
- 'avg_per_game': average per game/event in USD
- 'num_years': number of years in the contract
- 'duration': duration of the contract in years
- 'left': if the person left the team or streaming service before the contract expired.
- 'retired': if the person retired or not
- 'not_guar': if the contract is guaranteed or not
title: Largest sports contracts
